scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The majority of the photographs in this collection were created for publicity purposes by the Office of Public Affairs.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The photographs are arranged in three series and two accessions: I. Photographs of individuals, 1870-1972; II. Photographs of individuals, 1973-1995; III. Oversize, 1978.
